Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有人受害了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会发生这种事...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特司祭
