Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.61,0:00:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...按市里的规矩
